clinical_trials.eligibility_criteria:
Inclusion Criteria:

1. Subjects clearly understand and voluntarily participate in this study, sign the informed consent form and voluntarily comply with the study procedures;
2. Age ≥ 18 years and ≤ 70 years, male or female;
3. Endoscopic diagnosis of reflux esophagitis (LA classification criteria

Inclusion criteria;

-Proton pump inhibitor-resistant reflux esophagitis. (Patients who have mucosal breaks (erosions, ulcers) on endoscopy)

Exclusion criteria;

* Patients with a history of hypersensitivity to any ingredients of PARIET.
* Patients on atazanavir sulfate.
